Abstract = {How can companies take advantage of Large Language Models (LLMs) without
   taking security and compliance risks? A legitimate question, given the
   numerous and often free offerings on the market. One solution would be
   to integrate LLMs into the company's own technology landscape with a
   connection to the respective internal company data sources. This not
   only enables precise and context-related answers, but also facilitates
   the automation of processes. Figure 1: Retrieval Augmented Generation
   (RAG) explained schematically.},
